      "faqs": {
        "testQ": "What exactly does AiBreaker test?",
        "testA": "AiBreaker crawls your app like a real user on both desktop and mobile. It screens for broken UI flows, dead clicks, visual bugs, accessibility issues, and logic errors - then hands you a fix prompt for each one.",
        "installQ": "Do I need to install anything?",
        "installA": "Nope. Just paste your public URL and hit \"Run Audit.\" AiBreaker uses its own headless browser - no SDK, no code changes, no deploys required.",
        "differenceQ": "How is this different from Lighthouse or Playwright?",
        "differenceA": "Lighthouse measures performance. Playwright requires you to write scripts. AiBreaker does visual + behavioral QA with AI - no script writing, and it generates fix prompts automatically.",
        "cancelQ": "Can I cancel anytime?",
        "cancelA": "Yes. No contracts, no lock-in. Cancel from your billing settings and your plan ends at the next billing cycle. Your audit history stays available on the free tier.",
        "securityQ": "Is my site data secure?",
        "securityA": "We only audit publicly accessible pages. Screenshots and recordings are encrypted at rest and deleted after 30 days. We never access your source code unless you explicitly paste it in the Fix & Verify tier."
      }
